name: DeltaWaves
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: delta waves
des:
This skill plays an audio track to help you fall into a deep, restful sleep. You can control it with the usual voice commands like "pause", "resume", and "start over".

With over 90 million views on YouTube (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xQ6xgDI7Whc&t), this track has helped many people around the world. We hope it will help you, too!

Icon art designed by Freepik.(http://www.freepik.com).
Audio recording by Neuromancer courtesy of Tobacco Music Edition (https://equilibriummusicgroup.com/). This and other content can be found at:
https://www.youtube.com/meditationrelaxclub.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
